name: SACRED CATS SNIPPET I
description: Snippet from "A Chariot Drawn by Cats" Super 8mm shortfilm with original music from NYC jazzist Stan Zenkov.  Starring Hanna-Katarina, Daniela Farías and Benedek Mendoza. Sound On. KODAK EKTACHROME 100D Shot at Edward James surrealist garden, Xilitla, México, 2021.
